OL,3,C'We need to relieve suffering' -
OL,4,Creaction in South West to assisted
OL,5,Cdying vote
OL,7,FMPs have voted in favour of the
OL,8,Fassisted dying bill which will
OL,9,Flegalise the right for terminally ill
OL,10,Fpeople in England and Wales to end
OL,11,Ftheir own life with medical assistance.
OL,13,FIn an historic vote, MPs voted 314 to
OL,14,F219 in favour of the bill, backing the
OL,15,Fright for adults with less than six
OL,16,Fmonths to live to choose to end their
OL,17,Fown lives.
