OL,3,C'We need to relieve suffering' -
OL,4,Creaction in South West to assisted
OL,5,Cdying vote
OL,7,FIt came after an often highly
OL,8,Femotional debate, with impassioned
OL,9,Farguments here in the South West on
OL,10,Feither side.
OL,12,FPat Malone, from Bodmin, Cornwall,
OL,13,Fwhose father died from cancer in the
OL,14,F1990s, believes he should have been
OL,15,Fgiven the choice to end his life
OL,16,Fsooner.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
