OL,3,C'We need to relieve suffering' -
OL,4,Creaction in South West to assisted
OL,5,Cdying vote
OL,7,FHe said his father endured "appalling
OL,8,Fpain that couldn't be relieved" and
OL,9,Fwas left "a beaten husk of a man,
OL,10,Frolling around in a hospital bed
OL,11,Fwithout any dignity" before he died.
OL,13,FOn the other side of the debate is Dr
OL,14,FRachel Perry. She trained in Bristol
OL,15,Fand now works as an anaesthetist at
OL,16,FDerriford Hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
