OL,3,C'We need to relieve suffering' -
OL,4,Creaction in South West to assisted
OL,5,Cdying vote
OL,7,FShe argues that, as a doctor, she
OL,8,Ftrained to care for people, not to
OL,9,Foffer them the choice to die.
OL,11,FFriday's vote does not mean the bill
OL,12,Fimmediately becomes law as it will now
OL,13,Ftransfer to the House of Lords for
OL,14,Ffurther scrutiny.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
