OL,7,FThe upper chamber can make amendments
OL,8,Fto the bill and pass it back to MPs
OL,9,Fbut it is expected this process will
OL,10,Fhappen fairly quickly as the final
OL,11,Fdate they can currently consider a
OL,12,FPrivate Members' Bill in this
OL,13,Fparliamentary session is 11 July.
OL,15,FThere are several more stages of
OL,16,Fscrutiny in both chambers for the bill
OL,17,Fto go through before it heads to the
OL,18,FKing to receive royal assent and
OL,19,Fbecome law.
