OL,7,FEven with all of these processes it
OL,8,Fcould still be another four years
OL,9,Fbefore the first person in the UK is
OL,10,Fable to legally make use of assisted
OL,11,Fdying services as the bill allows this
OL,12,Ftime for the government to work out
OL,13,Fhow it is implemented.
